<h2> Open Office Hours</h2>
I have open office hours, primarily intended for Ph.D. students in CSE at UM (you do not have to be my student to see me). They can be used for just getting acquainted, general career discussion, chat about research, dealing with challenges in doing a Ph.D., or anything else. To reserve a slot, please book <a href="https://calendar.app.google/eydQLbaeeETnKWZBA"> here</a>.  Reach me on email or Google chat if needed.

